 "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018543, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Ay kanoosh, ar kanoosh, araha-shash at-beesa-faneekh, ya mattaroon, qaryaa laseewun, ma o ma sooma, teetasa loos, khabzoos, masfaqees, masa mawush, ifratee-ush, lateefo-kush latee-foosh haaza haaza…", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay kanoosh, ar kanoosh, araha-shash at-beesa-faneekh, ya mattaroon, qaryaa laseewun, ma o ma sooma, teetasa loos, khabzoos, masfaqees, masa mawush, ifratee-ush, lateefo-kush latee-foosh haaza haaza…", "Urdu": "اے کنوش، ارکنوش، ارہ شش عطبیفنیخ، یا مططرون، قریا لسیوں، ما و ما سوما طیطسالوس، خبظوس، مسفقیں، مسامعوش، افرطیعوش، لطیفکش، لطیفوش ھٰذا ھٰذا۔۔۔", "RArabic": "SORRY NOT AVAILABLE", "ArabicText1": "اَیْ كَنُوْشَ اَلرْكَنُوْشَ، اَرَهَ شَشْ عَطْبِیْسَفَنِیْخَ یَا مَطْطَرُوْنَ قَرْیَالَسِیْوُنْ مَا وَمَا سُوْمَا، سُوْمَا طِیْطَسَالُوْسَ خَبْطُوْسَ مَسْفَقِیْسَ، مَسَا مَعْوُشْ اِفْرَطِیْعُوْشَ لَطِیْفُكُشْ لَطِیْفُوْشَ هٰذَا هٰذَا۔۔۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018544, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "And you were not on the western side when We revealed to Musa his commandment, and you were not among the witnesses. Get out by the order of Allah O the vicious by the honour of Allah, lord of the worlds, or else you will be imprisoned. Be away from here, as you have no right to move freely over here. Go forth surely you are one of the abject ones. Go out as you are degraded and rebuked and stoned as Allah had cursed the violators of Sabbath and command of Allah shall be executed, blessed is Allah the best of the creators.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur tum Magribee simt (West side) mein us waqt na thay jab ham ne Moosa (a.s) ko apna hukm diya, aur na tum us waqt gawaho’n mein thay. Ay maloon us dil se qudrat’e Khuda se nikal ja nikal ja, tamaam jahano ke Parwardigaar ki izzat ke darr se nikal ja, warna tu qaid kar liya jaayega. Yahan se dur hoja kyu’n keh tujhe yahan chalne phir ne ka haq nahin, nikal ja keh tu zaleel hai qaabil’e mazammat, phitkaar zadah aur aisa laanati ho kar jaise Khuda ne hafte (Saturday) waale logo’n par laanat ki thi, Aur Allah ka hukm jaari hi huwa karta hai. Aise badboo daar, ay sada (badboo-daar), ay soora (be-faiyda) nikal ja keh yahan posheedah Isme Aazam ka hisaar (qila) hai, ay tatroon, ay taroon, maraawun. Beh-tareen paiyda karne waala paak o bartar hai.", "Urdu": "اور تم مغربی سمت میں اس وقت نہ تھے جب ہم نے موسٰیؑ کو اپنا حکم دیا، اور نہ تم اس وقت گوا ہوں میں تھے۔ اے ملعوں اس دل سے قدرتِ خدا سے نکل جا نکل جا! تمام جہانوں کے پروردگار کی عزّت کے ڈر سے نکل جا، ورنہ تو قید کر لیا جائے گا۔ یہاں سے دور ہوجا کیونکہ تجھے یہاں چلنے پھرنے کا حق نہیں، نکل جا کہ تو ذلیل ہے قابل مذمت، پھٹکار زدہ اور ایسا لعنتی ہو کر جیسے خدانے ہفتہ والے لوگوں پر لعنت کی تھی، اور اللہ کا حکم جاری ہی ہوا کرتا ہے، ایسے بدبودار، اے سڑا، اے سورا نکل جا کہ یہاں پوشیدہ اسم اعظم کا حصار ہے، اے ططرون اے طرعون، مراعون، بہتریں پیدا کرنے والا پاک و برتر ہے۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَمَا كُنْتَ بِجَانِبِ الْغَرْبِیِّ اِذْ قَضَیْنَا اِلٰی مُوْسَی الْآمْرَ وَمَا كُنْتَ مِنَ الشَّاهِدِیْنَ اُخْرُجْ بِقُدْرَۃِ اللهِ مِنْهَا اَیُّهَا اللَّعِیْنُ بِعِزَّۃِ اللهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ اُخْرُجْ مِنْهَا وَاِلَّا كُنْتَ مِنَ الْمَسْجُوْنِیْنَ اُخْرُجْ مِنْهَا فَمَا یَكُوْنُ لَكَ اَنْ تَتَكَبَّرَ فِیْهَا فَاخْرُجْ اِنَّكَ مِنَ الصَّاغِرِیْنَ اُخْرُجْ مِنْهَا مُذْئُوْمًا مَدْحُوْرًا مَلْعُوْنًا كَمَا لَعَنَّا اَصْحَابَ السَّبْتِ وَكَانَ اَمْرُ اللهِ مَفْعُوْلًا اُخْرُجْ یَا ذَوِی الْمَحْزُوْنَ اُخْرُجْ یَا سُوْرًا یَا سُوْرًا سُوْرٌ بِالْاِسْمِ الْمَخْزُوْنِ یَا طِطَرُوْنَ طَرْعُوْنَ مَرَاعُوْنَ تَبَارَكَ اللهُ اَحْسَنُ الْخَالِقِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1018545, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O life, O life in the name of Allah who is eternal which is written on the forehead of Israfeel be away from the one who has worn this talisman whether you are jin or fairy, devil or devils, male or female, male magician or female magician, ghost or female ghost or any other thing who plays with the son of Adam or Eve. Except for Allah the exalted and high there is no power or strength. And O Allah! Send blessings on Mohammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) the pure and infallible ones.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay haya ay haya, zindah o bar-qaraar Khuda ke us naam ki wajah se jo Israfeel (a.s) ki peshaani par likkha hai us taaweez waale ke paas se dur hoja, khwah (chahe) woh Jinn ho ya Pari, Shaitaan ho ya shaitaani mard ham-zaad ho ya aurat, jaadoogar ho ya jadoo garni, bhoot ho ya bhootni ya har woh jaadoogar jo farzand’e Aadam (a.s) aur dukhtaraan Hawwa se khel-te hai. Buzurg o bartar Allah ke siwa koi saaheb’e quwwat o taaqat nahin. Aur ay Allah! Hazrat Muhammad’e Mustafa (s.a.w.a) aur unki tamaam paak o paakeezah aur Maasoom Aulaad (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma.", "Urdu": " اے ہیا اے ہیا، زندہ و برقرار خدا کے اس نام کی وجہ سے جو اسرافیل کی پیشانی پر لکھا ہے اس تعویذ والے کے پاس سے دور ہوجا، خواہ وہ جنّ ہو یا پری، شیطان ہو یا شیطانی مرد ہمزاد ہو یا عورت، جادوگر ہو یا جادوگرنی، بھوت ہو یا بھتنی یا ہر وہ جادوگر جو فرزند آدمؑ اور دختران حوّا سے کھیلتے ہیں، بزرگ و برتر اللہ کے سوا کوئی صاحب قوت و طاقت نہیں، اور اے اللہ! حضر محمد مصطفٰیؐ اور ان کی تمام پاک و پاجیزہ اور معصوم اولادؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "یَا هَیَا یَا هَیَا شَرَاهِیًّا حَیًّا قَیُّوْمًا بِالْاِسْمِ الْمَكْتُوْبِ عَلٰی جَبْهَۃِ اِسْرَافِیْلَ اُطُرُدُوْا عَنْ صَاحِبِ هٰذَا الْكِتَابِ كُلَّ جِنِیٍّ وَجِنِیَّۃٍ وَشَیْطَانٍ وَشَیْطَانَۃٍ وَتَابِعٍ وَتَابِعَۃٍ وَسَاحِرٍ وَسَاحِرَۃٍ وَغَوْلٍ وَغَوْلَۃٍ وَكُلَّ مُتَعَبِّثٍ وَعَابِثٍ یَعْبَثُ بِاِبْنِ آدَمَ وَبَنَاتِ حَوَّا وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّۃَ اِلَّا بِاللهِ الْعَلِیِّ الْعَظِیْمِ وَصَلَّی اللهُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ اَجْمَعِیْنَ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ الْمَعْصُوْمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null